                <h4> Organisation Edit </h4>
                <p>
                    To modify organisation details, click on the organisation on the main menu the form below will appear, Click on the name of the organisation you want to modify
                </p>
                <div class="ImageContainer">   <img class="Image" src="~/Images/OrganisationList.JPG" /> </div>
                <p>
                    The form below will appear containing details of the orgainisation which you can now modify.
                </p>

                <div class="ImageContainer">
                    <img class="Image" src="~/Images/OrganisationEditForm.JPG" />
                    <div />

                    <p>Press the save button to register the changes </p>

